\frac{\angle EAG}{\angle GAF} = \frac{\mathrm{sector}(HAG)}{\mathrm{sector}(GAK)}<\frac{\mathrm{area}(\triangle EAG)}{\mathrm{area}(\triangle GAF)}=\frac{\frac{1}{2}|AF||EG|}{\frac{1}{2}|AF||GF|}=\frac{|EG|}{|GF|}
